going beyond the basics, and I

00:02:05.516 --> 00:02:07.306 A:middle
want to start by focusing in on

00:02:07.306 --> 00:02:09.966 A:middle
this one word, usable.

00:02:11.116 --> 00:02:13.276 A:middle
Usable is great, making sure

00:02:13.276 --> 00:02:14.656 A:middle
that all of the content of your

00:02:14.656 --> 00:02:16.116 A:middle
app is even visible to an

00:02:16.116 --> 00:02:17.606 A:middle
