00:20:33.666 --> 00:20:35.016 A:middle
can leverage to resolve them.

00:20:36.246 --> 00:20:37.906 A:middle
From Bhavya's audit, we found

00:20:37.906 --> 00:20:39.276 A:middle
some issues with our carousel.

00:20:40.056 --> 00:20:41.196 A:middle
We could get to the favorite and

