00:22:38.196 --> 00:22:39.446 A:middle
But combining them would cut

00:22:39.446 --> 00:22:41.096 A:middle
that in half and makes

00:22:41.096 --> 00:22:43.026 A:middle
navigation much, much faster.

00:22:44.476 --> 00:22:45.796 A:middle
It makes more sense to group

00:22:45.796 --> 00:22:46.946 A:middle
these labels together as a

00:22:46.946 --> 00:22:48.496 A:middle
single element so that I

00:22:48.496 --> 00:22:49.586 A:middle
understand the relationship

00:22:49.586 --> 00:22:50.716 A:middle
between label and value.

00:22:51.346 --> 00:22:52.406 A:middle
We again can use UI

00:22:52.406 --> 00:22:53.656 A:middle
