00:24:08.356 --> 00:24:09.626 A:middle
to the user as what's going to

00:24:09.626 --> 00:24:11.116 A:middle
happen when they activate that

00:24:11.116 --> 00:24:13.666 A:middle
action, and a target selector

00:24:13.666 --> 00:24:15.446 A:middle
relationship, which will execute

00:24:15.446 --> 00:24:17.586 A:middle
the action in your code.

00:24:17.806 --> 00:24:19.056 A:middle
So we'll make that whole shelter

00:24:19.056 --> 00:24:20.696 A:middle
